Quantum and Woody v1 was an extremely funny and silly parody of superhero comics, from the brain of Christopher Priest with art by Mark Bright. Billed as &quot;The World's Worst Superhero Team&quot;, these two idiots (estranged and reunited friends from childhood) come together ostensibly to battle evil with their fancy new powers obtained through accident - as is the classic trope. In reality, they wisecrack a lot and mess things up pretty often. The series ran for 17 issues proper, and came back for 5 more - one of which was jokingly labeled as issue 32 (to hold as a placemarker for the publication to catch up). Unfortunately it was canceled, but there was a special produced as well as a number zero issue. Now that the series has returned, it is the perfect time to catch up with this comedy classic!

This torrent contains all issues 00-21 + 32 of the first volume, along with the GOAT H.A.E.D.U.S. special and some unpublished artwork and a script as well. Everything except for those two latter items are digital, courtesy of BlurPixel-Empire. Thanks to them for these great new copies, and please seed - enjoy! :-)
